reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Game Changer for My Work and Play!
reviews.reviewText: can’t say enough about the Levn USB Headset UH002 – it’s truly a game changer in the world of audio accessories. As someone who uses headsets for both work and play, I was searching for a versatile and high-quality option, and this headset delivered beyond my expectations.First and foremost, the audio quality is outstanding. Whether I’m on a Zoom call with colleagues, immersing myself in a gaming session, or enjoying my favorite music, the sound is crisp, clear, and immersive. The noise-canceling feature is a true blessing, blocking out distracting background noises and ensuring I stay focused on what matters.Comfort is paramount when it comes to headsets, and the Levn UH002 does not disappoint. The adjustable headband and cushioned ear cups provide hours of comfort, and I can wear it for extended periods without any discomfort. It’s a true blessing for those long workdays or marathon gaming sessions.The built-in microphone is of exceptional quality, ensuring that my voice comes through loud and clear during calls or in-game communication. No more awkward moments of repeating myself or asking others to do so.What sets this headset apart is its versatility. The USB connection is incredibly convenient, and it’s plug-and-play, which means no complicated setups or software installations. It’s compatible with a wide range of devices, making it a fantastic all-in-one solution.In summary, the Levn USB Headset UH002 is a fantastic investment for anyone in need of a reliable and versatile audio accessory. Its exceptional audio quality, comfort, and compatibility make it a must-have for both work and play. Say goodbye to background noise and discomfort, and say hello to an elevated audio experience. I wholeheartedly recommend the Levn UH002 to anyone seeking a premium USB headset. You won’t be disappointed!

reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Another great product from Levn.The ear cushions are so soft and that makes me feel extremely comfortable wearing it. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Long but worth reading HONEST review. CSR edition.
reviews.reviewText: I bought this headset initially for customer service rep job, wfh. While it is a great headset for entertainment like watching movie, listening to music, the volume is fantastic! BUT, for work when in a call w customers, even if I put the volume on max it doesn't sound as good as it was when I’m just using it for listening to a music or watching videos online. It sounds low-mid vol even if it’s already on max volume. I am not sure what’s the reason behind it (not sure if it’s bc I’m on a 3rd party software for work or what but yeah, there’s that).Another key point is, I use this headphones for 8hrs of my job, the cushion on the ear is not the greatest and it makes the side of my ear hurt by wearing it for a long period of time. (+As someone who wears glasses, I have to lift up the thing that rests on the side of the ear cause it hurts after period of time).The quality of the mic/audio is great. Callers can hear me clear for the most part, no static, doesn’t get weird comments anymore like I sound like I’m in a tunnel or on speaker even if I’m not (heard these comments when I was still using a gaming headphones that was built for good sound but not so much for the mic since gaming is a whole other thing that doesn’t necessarily require users to speak, LOL).Overall, I’d say it’s a 50/50, it’s good for its price but for the sole purpose of why I bought the item, it’s not the best in terms of comfortability & technicality w the volume “work wise as csr using 3rd party sofetware” but I guess it will do since I already bought it and it’s doable after all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Superior quality and comfort
reviews.reviewText: I chanced upon this company by accident and am so glad I did! I now have three of their headsets and love all of them! Wired headsets are more reliable and easy to use for zoom meetings when i am at my desk. I like the bluetooth ones when I am on the go, and i use those even biking and kayaking! But this one, like all the products this company makes is of superior quality, great sound, easy use, and sooooo comfortable. It is really pretty amazing how inexpensive they are. I do not normally expect such a great product for so little money. I hope this company expands into other electronics. For example, I would love a reliable back lit keyboard for my iPad mini 6. I am hoping the great engineers in this company would consider expanding their product line in that way! Grateful for their products and their excellent and personal customer service.
